videos.headline: Alec Ridder leaps to snag heavily guarded Cincy TD
videos.description: Cincinnati's Alec Pierce works hard in the end zone to pull down a nine-yard touchdown pass from Desmond Ridder.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Alec Ridder leaps to snag heavily guarded Cincy TD) 2021/10/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincy's Jerome Ford punches in 8-yard TD
videos.description: Jerome Ford runs eight yards into the end zone to give Cincinnati a 17-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cincy's Jerome Ford punches in 8-yard TD) 2021/10/8 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincy starts second half hot with 75-yard TD
videos.description: Jerome Ford runs it 75 yards to the house to help Cincy start the second half with a bang.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cincy starts second half hot with 75-yard TD) 2021/10/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincy capitalizes off of Temple's muffed punt with 38-yard TD
videos.description: Desmond Ridder connects with Tyler Scott, who zig-zags his way into the end zone after Temple muffs the punt for the second time.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cincy capitalizes off of Temple's muffed punt with 38-yard TD) 2021/10/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincy goes up big on Ridder's third TD pass
videos.description: Desmond Ridder tosses his third touchdown pass of the night to give the Bearcats a 45-3 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cincy goes up big on Ridder's third TD pass) 2021/10/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ethan Wright turns on the jets for 58-yard Cincy TD
videos.description: Ethan Wright smokes Temple's defense for a 58-yard house call.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ethan Wright turns on the jets for 58-yard Cincy TD) 2021/10/08 ESHEET
